# Windows Herd + Git Bash (laravel13.x)

**Full lessons:** `docs/EXAMPLE_DEV_LESSONS.md` ‚Äî read before new `examples/*` work.

## PHP is never bare `php` in Git Bash

| Do | Don't |
|----|--------|
| `export PATH="/d/laravel13.x/bin:$PATH"` | Assume `php` works |
| `/c/Users/vitou/.config/herd/bin/php.bat artisan ‚Ä¶` | Install separate PHP |

## New example (`bin/new-example <slug> "Name"`)

1. Creates Laravel + Spec-Kit + **herd link** ‚Üí `http://<slug>.test`
2. Ends with **`bin/verify-example <slug>`** ‚Äî must pass before telling user "done"
3. User browser: **`APP_URL` from `.env`**, not `:5173`
4. `npm run dev` = Vite only when `APP_URL` ends with `.test`

## Known failures (fix, don't re-investigate)

| Error | Script |
|-------|--------|
| `vendor/autoload.php` missing / `npm run dev` dies on artisan | `cd examples/<slug> && composer install` |
| Herd 500 `getaddrinfo for redis failed` | `.env` has Docker `REDIS_HOST=redis` ‚Äî use `.env.example` locals: `CACHE_STORE=file`, `SESSION_DRIVER=file`, `QUEUE_CONNECTION=sync`, `REDIS_HOST=127.0.0.1` |
| `npm run dev` starts `artisan serve` not Vite-only | Set `APP_URL=http://<slug>.test` + `herd link <slug>` |
| Unsupported cipher / APP_KEY | `./bin/fix-example-app-key <slug>` |
| 500 after scaffold | `./bin/verify-example <slug>` then fix script |
| `php` not found | `export PATH="/d/laravel13.x/bin:$PATH"` |
| Docker port already allocated | Change host port in `docker-compose.yml` (e.g. `8089:8080`) |
| Docker 500, missing encryption key | Add `env_file: .env` to compose ‚Äî container needs `APP_KEY` |
| Docker Desktop not running | Start Docker Desktop before `docker compose up` |
| ngrok ‚Üí Herd **404 Site not found** (OAuth) | `ngrok http 127.0.0.1:80 --traffic-policy-file ngrok-traffic-policy.yml` ‚Äî not `ngrok http http://<slug>.test`; see `docs/EXAMPLE_DEV_LESSONS.md` |

**Never** write `APP_KEY` from `artisan key:generate --show` (ANSI colors break encryption).

## Agent checklist

1. Run commands with `bin/php` or PATH export; show output.
2. After scaffold: `verify-example` must pass.
3. Tell user exact `http://<slug>.test` ‚Äî not localhost:5173/8000 unless Herd failed.
4. Do not re-scaffold MVPs in `docs/SESSION_STATE.md`.
5. Committed `.env` in `examples/*` from `new-example` ‚Äî use `fix-example-app-key` if corrupted.

## Quick verify

```bash
export PATH="/d/laravel13.x/bin:$PATH"
./bin/verify-example <slug>
```
